Package: Biosurvmet
Type: Package
Title: A Biomarker Validation approach for predicting Survival using Metabolomics Signatures 
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
       person("Olajumoke","Owokotomo",email="olajumoke.owokotomo@uhasselt.be",role=c("aut","cre")),
       person("Ziv","Shkedy",email="ziv.shkedy@uhasselt.be",role="aut"))
Maintainer: Olajumoke Owokotomo <olajumoke.owokotomo@uhasselt.be>
Description: Predicting patients Survival using Metabolomics Signatures. The package use the metabolomics signature and other prognostic factors
   as classifier for dividing the patients into low and high risk groups. The classifier is a linear combination of the signature and the prognostic factor and/or treatment effect.    It implements several
    advanced classifier techniques and validation procedures. It also implements reduction of the metabolomics data with various reduction method and cross validation approach to investigate the mostly selected metabolic signature.
URL: https://www.uhasselt.be/fiche?email=olajumoke.owokotomo#fiche
